snippet.title: Amber Heard vs Johnny Depp Bots | Adam Waldman, Rose McGowan v BlackCube, Brittany Murphy, Elon Musk
snippet.description:
MOVIE: Amber Heard vs Johnny Depp's Violence & Double Agents | Rose McGowan vs BlackCube... Many actresses were on BlackCube's hit list. Although Elon Musk rushed in to Help after high-profile violence, Amber Heard faces Depp's agent Adam Waldman - of Steele Dossier, Oligarch Deripaska organized crime, and targeted Assange for election interference. Support Amber Heard's Life!

"What happened on private jets and islands between Amber Heard and Johnny Depp?" Was it really broadcasted, or was it silenced & twisted?
Why is Amber Heard's story beginning to sound like a "007 Flemming's Novel" to an Artificial Intelligence auditor?

Social Bot Influence/Disinformation Operations:
With death threats & Social Bots online in a 21st Century tech story - 
Tens of Thousands of New Accounts harm AH -
made 134,000 Tweets just in 2020 against Amber as seen in Social Network Analysis. 

Amber Heard is progressive - supported by ACLU, Cherie Blair, & VP Kamala Harris.
"In 2016, the target was Hillary Clinton. In the case of review bombing, the target was female-fronted films." - The Geek Buzz, July 28, 2020
Webscraping Twitter on Election 2016 night shows Trump mentioned 3-4 times more than Hillary Clinton - Bots.

Rose McGowan states Harvey Weinstein hired agents who pretended they were Journalists & in victim's support groups. They terrified Dozens of Actresses.

Waldman refers to homeland security as Depp & Waldman claim Amber created a 'dossier.'  10 years ago, in parallels Actress Brittany Murphy & Julia Davis were targeted, severely monitored for testifying on border control issues of homeland security.

Brittany Murphy lost her roles in Happy Feet 2 and died suddenly.
Amber Heard is targeted to remove her from Aquaman 2 and to kill her.

Likely monitoring pages occurs against Amber Heard online using AI Bots & SEO.
Bots appear to use "I am" Persona Dialogue - Open Source on Github 2017-2020. ILM/Alex Context Dialogues go beyond Google's BERT for Previous Text Dialogues - NLU/NLG, Sentiment (Emotion) Positive/Negative like campaign bots.
Ironically, Elon Musk's OpenAI GPT-2 & GPT-3 - likely is being used against his ex girlfriend, Amber Heard.

Witnesses have been threatened with death, as alerted to nearly 2 years ago when an alleged partner of ex-staff claimed Depp's agents wanted to make lies about Amber Heard's trips to Tijuana for Amnesty International & targeting her Humanitarian Work. 
Their goal is to destroy her & it was the tip of the iceberg.

J. Depp is incited by audience to terminate President Trump in his suggestion. 
Then we see Amber Heard (Black & White) & Elon Musk.

In 2016, Amber and IO finally called the police after fearing for her life. 
Officers went to Depp's 5 Penthouses in Downtown Los Angeles which we show with a pool rooftop, numerous rooms, and abusive paintings of girls on the walls which people walk by and ignore. 
- Right next to this extreme wealth, are slums of Los Angeles.

Audio clips, which were cut out of timed leaks, from Incredibly Incredible's channel - https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCjKNc-woAlnxt0H-yJ8RXJg​ - are shown to provide context to Coercive Control. 
Depp harms Amber Heard with Coercive Control - understood about domestic abuse in Australia, New Zealand, & United Kingdom. 
A woman in Australia who eventually called the police is told by a corrupt officer that she shouldn't have texted, in writing, about her husband's temper during intoxication that pushes him over thee edge as it would trigger an investigation.
United Kingdom: 
Amber WON in NGN trial proving she was a victim of violence in at least 12 out of 14 incidents.

"Hey @mariannaspring [BBC], after I discovered the connection between Johnny Depp attorney Adam Waldman & a Vladimir Putin-connected Russian oligarch 16 months ago, I postulated the theory Depp's team was using bots to influence public opinion on his case." - The Geek Buzz, July 28, 2020

"Twitter can be a hostile place,” Jennifer Robinson says. “The online attacks in respect of Amber have been far worse than anything I experienced during the Julian Assange case.” - Financial Times
Jennifer Robinson, Assange's lawyer of 10 years, was hired by Amber Heard. Waldman met with Assange to target him at least 7 times. 
We show a political clip showing texts between Waldman and Senator Warner of Virginia about Steele's dossier.

"...it's a hoax by Adam "former lobbyist for Russian Putin Lackey Oleg Deripaska who sought complete immunity in the US Senate Russian 2016 hacking hearings" Waldman." - The Geek Buzz, July 29, 2020
(Bots & Personality?)
